<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
  <head>
    <meta http-equiv="Content-Type" content="text/html; charset=utf-8" />
    <style>
      /* Email-safe CSS styles */
      .container {
        max-width: 600px;
        margin: 0 auto;
        font-family: Arial, sans-serif;
        line-height: 1.6;
        color: #333;
      }
      .header {
        background-color: #0d7377;
        color: white;
        padding: 20px;
        text-align: center;
      }
      .content {
        padding: 30px 20px;
        background-color: #ffffff;
      }
      .button {
        display: inline-block;
        background-color: #0d7377;
        color: white;
        padding: 12px 24px;
        text-decoration: none;
        border-radius: 5px;
        margin: 20px 0;
      }
      .footer {
        background-color: #f8f9fa;
        padding: 20px;
        text-align: center;
        font-size: 14px;
        color: #666;
      }
    </style>
  </head>
  <body>
    <div class="container">
      <div class="header">
        <h1>Welcome to Startonaut!</h1>
      </div>
      <div class="content">
        <h2>Hello <%= @user.email_address %>!</h2>
        <p>Thank you for joining <strong>Startonaut</strong>! We're excited to have you on board.</p>
        <p>With Startonaut, you can:</p>
        <ul>
          <li>Organize your bookmarks with tags</li>
          <li>Automatically fetch page titles and favicons</li>
          <li>Create a personalized bookmark collection</li>
          <li>Access your bookmarks from anywhere</li>
        </ul>
        <p>Ready to get started?</p>
        <a href="<%= @url %>" class="button">Start Bookmarking</a>
        <p>If you have any questions or need help, feel free to reach out to us.</p>
        <p>Happy bookmarking!</p>
        <p>The Startonaut Team</p>
      </div>
      <div class="footer">
        <p>This email was sent to <%= @user.email_address %> because you signed up for a Startonaut account.</p>
        <p>Â© <%= Date.current.year %> Startonaut. All rights reserved.</p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </body>
